tinygltf is header-only and can be used from CMake via:

    find_path(TINYGLTF_INCLUDE_DIR "tiny_gltf.h")
    target_include_directories(main PRIVATE "${TINYGLTF_INCLUDE_DIR}")

To use RapidJSON instead of the default nlohmann-json, add:

    target_compile_definitions(main PRIVATE TINYGLTF_USE_RAPIDJSON)

To use tinygltf without stb, add:

    target_compile_definitions(main PRIVATE TINYGLTF_NO_STB_IMAGE TINYGLTF_NO_STB_IMAGE_WRITE)
